snippet.title: DISNEY SING IT: Party Hits -- game play trailer
snippet.description:
DISNEY SING IT: Party Hits -- game play trailer

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/disneyinteractivestudios

Available now: http://amzn.to/aM9lnf

Have a blast with your friends as you sing along to chart-topping pop hits, practice with celebrity vocal coach Demi Lovato, and update your game with downloadable tracks with DISNEY SING IT: PARTY HITS!  

Available for PlayStation®3 & Wii™ console.  ESRB Rating:  E with Mild Lyrics, Mild Suggestive Themes and Mild Violence. 

***
More Disney video games...

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8puWFqVJAdA&feature=channel

Visit the other Disney Interactive Studios YouTube channel: http://www.youtube.com/disneyvideogames
